Package edu.cs.uga.DatabaseTermProject.model

Class Product

java.lang.Object
edu.cs.uga.DatabaseTermProject.model.Product
public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a product. Each product contains a id, category, categoryID, price value, average review score, and the number of products sold.
